data.title: Sanya, Hainan ZIP Code - China
data.meta_description: Chose an area inside prefecture-level city Sanya the province Hainan to find the correct ZIP Code. Select one area - Ding'an, Wenchang, Qionghai, Wanning, Tunchang, Danzhou, Lingao, Chengmai, Sanya, Zhongsha Islands and Sea Area, Xisha, Wuzhishan, Tongshi, Baoting Lizu-Miaozu, Lingshui Lizu, Ledong Lizu, Dongfang, Changjiang Lizu, Baisha Lizu, Qiongzhong Lizu-Miaozu, Nansha - to finally find out the correspondent ZIP Code.
data.text: The Prefecture-level City (地级市 dìjíshì) of Sanya, Hainan has 21 differents ZIP Codes. Check the map below to check your ZIP Code.
